    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You're adapted to life in the badlands of southern Seillia. In predominantly sandy or rocky terrain, you can ignore 5 feet of movement penalty caused by difficult terrain or greater difficult terrain.</p><p>You can always use the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.ust1jJSCZQUhBZIz]{Take Cover} action when you are within desert or badlands terrain to gain cover, even if you're not next to an obstacle you can Take Cover behind.</p><p>You do not know Liluathan as a benefit of being faerefolk. Instead, you know Baltian.</p>",
